ts/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b2e0c815c0608536c7d23814eddea3ca1f1b7b","tid":1433676,"uid":302750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:57:24.000Z","msg":"我都聽過有果啲激光帽<br />\n不過我自已覺得如果本身仲有幾多頭髮<br />\n戴帽果陣啲頭髮會遮住啲激光<br />\n因爲啲激光好似要照住頭皮先有效<br />\n所以好似梳會好啲<br />\n但係就要比耐性自己慢慢梳"},{"pid":"ab093f0bba3117d1604eb566d568598419a0f0a8","tid":1433676,"uid":204670,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"食住propecia藥同查住minoxidil 5%水先, keep住唔惡化太勁, 之後甩定左去植髮, 睇d圖, 人地係後腦拎毛囊幾性感, 紅哂, 想大大力R落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jjmW7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jjmW7a.jpg&h=ad619d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5cYOB7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5cYOB7b.jpg&h=6f417865&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e57d7c006bec197c13f9a91cd26536fe5e31c6b","tid":1433676,"uid":117811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"我最近都甩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}